 9th . This morn we pack up move off from Halloy-Pernoi toward the fire line , it was a scorch hot morn , the dust was someth aw far wors than the march which was quit stiff enough for anyon . We pass a lot of our artilleri , the 5th Brigad on the way back they did not get the cut up we did , we had a good long spell on the grass while the Artilleri pass us . We are now in billet about 6 mile from Halloy . Receiv quit a budget of letter yesterday , Greta photo among them how she has chang .
